      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2548 - Abu Ayyub narrated from Abu ‘Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Indeed, one of them combines (qarana) and drives (hady), and so I leave him as a consequence (punishment) for what he has done.\""
